RConfigurationFilesProvider
public abstract class AbstractRConfigurationFilesProvider extends AbstractRCompatibilityCheckerAndCopierUser
This abstract class defines configuration file providers which use compatibility checker (InterfaceCompatibilityChecker) and configurator (InterfaceConfigurator) to operate.
